data.title: IIHF 2022 Ice Hockey World Championship: team Finland make it to the semifinals!
data.meta_description: Team Finland are in the semifinals after winning 4-2 Vs Slovakia. Sweden were leading 3-0 Vs Canada at the end of the second period, but have finally been defeated 4-3 (overtime). The semis (May the 28th) are Finland-USA and Canada-Czech Republic. IIHF.com
